Articles.Content: Has anyone got any mods for 0.13.3? I cannot find any. I have the full version but my cousin can't because he cannot buy it. So any mods for ksp 0.13.3? Like landing legs and new engines?

The one major problem with mods in the demo, is that the demo has no ability to handle the plugins.

Just about any mod that does not use plugins should be fine, and even many parts from mods that do have plugins are still usable, but plugin functionality will fail.

Two of my favorite packs for 0.13.3 are the Downunder aerospace pack and the White Monkey kitchen supplies pack, both are still available here in the add-on section

White monkey pack.
